# Shorebird release strategy (RF Logger)

**App dir:** `app/` ┬╖ **app_id:** `c4217590-d971-4cca-9ed2-e804dc47453f` ┬╖ **pkg:** `com.repairfully.logger`
**One command:** `./tools/ship.ps1` (app dir se chalao)
**Clean baseline:** `2.0.0+8` (pehli release jo `--no-tree-shake-icons` se bani тАФ isi line par patches reliable). Purani lines (`2.0.0+7` aur pehle) tree-shake ON se bani thi тЖТ un par naya patch unpatchable.

---

## Sabse zaroori 3 rules

1. **`--no-tree-shake-icons` HAMESHA** тАФ release AUR patch dono me. Warna `MaterialIcons-Regular.otf` ka icon-set badalne par `UnpatchableChangeException` aata hai aur patch phone tak nahi pohanchta. `ship.ps1` me yeh baked hai.
2. **Patch ka `--release-version` = phone par installed RELEASE version** (EXACT). Guess mat karo. Mismatch = patch kabhi nahi dikhega.
3. **+build aur version saath chalao.** Purana confusion (`1.0.3+5 тЖТ 1.0.4+6`, do `1.0.4+x` lines) isi se aaya. Release mode `ship.ps1` sirf `+build` bump karta hai тАФ clean line.

---

## Decision tree

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  F[Sir bole "fixes"] --> Q{Kya badla?}
  Q -->|Sirf Dart/lib| P[PATCH]
  Q -->|android/ ios/ assets/ pubspec deps / flutter ver| R[RELEASE]
  P --> P1["ship.ps1 -Mode patch<br/>--no-tree-shake-icons<br/>--release-version = phone wali"]
  R --> R1["ship.ps1 -Mode release<br/>+build bump + APK + reinstall"]
  P1 --> P2[Phone: app poora band -> kholo -> dobara kholo]
  R1 --> R2[adb install -r APK]
```

| Change type | Action | Version |
|---|---|---|
| Dart-only (lib/) | `patch` | koi bump nahi |
| android/, ios/, assets/, pubspec deps, launcher icon, gradle, Flutter ver | `release` | `+build` bump |
| Shorebird `UnpatchableChange`/asset diff bole | `release` (us release ne tree-shake fix nahi liya tha) | `+build` bump |

---

## ship.ps1 usage

```powershell
# Dart-only fix -> newest active release ko patch (release-version auto-detect)
./tools/ship.ps1 -Mode patch

# Khaas release line target karni ho
./tools/ship.ps1 -Mode patch -ReleaseVersion 2.0.0+8

# Native/asset change -> nayi release + APK + (device ho to) auto install
./tools/ship.ps1 -Mode release

# git dekh kar khud decide kare
./tools/ship.ps1 -Mode auto

# Safe test (kuch upload nahi)
./tools/ship.ps1 -Mode patch -DryRun

# Changelog ke saath (auto <release>:<patch> marker + flutter analyze verify)
./tools/ship.ps1 -Mode patch -Changelog "Fix: gallery crash`n- thumbnail null guard"
```

- Device disconnected ho to script block nahi hota тАФ publish karke install command print karta hai.
- shorebird.bat ka "long paths" warning ignore тАФ success `$LASTEXITCODE` se decide hota hai.

---

## Changelog (kaise dikhe phone par)

- `app/lib/services/update_service.dart` тЖТ `latestChangelog` me **`<release>:<patch>`** marker rakho, e.g. `2.0.0+8:0 тАФ ...` (abhi yahi set hai).
- Device patch number badalne par hi banner dikhata hai (`consumePendingChangelog`). Patch apply hua = changelog naya. Patch apply nahi hua = changelog bhi nahi (downstream symptom).
- `ship.ps1 -Changelog "..."` yeh marker khud set karta hai.

---

## Verify commands (Sir ke liye)

```powershell
# Server par kaunsi releases + patches
& "C:\Users\DELL\.shorebird\bin\shorebird.bat" releases list
& "C:\Users\DELL\.shorebird\bin\shorebird.bat" patches list --release-version 2.0.0+8

# Phone par actually kaunsa version (device connect hone par)
$env:PATH = "$env:LOCALAPPDATA\Android\Sdk\platform-tools;$env:PATH"
adb devices
adb shell dumpsys package com.repairfully.logger | findstr versionName
```

**Agar phone ka versionName/build != patch ki release-version тЖТ wahi root cause hai. Pehle us release ka APK install karo, tabhi OTA patch dikhega.**

---

## Quick troubleshoot

| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| Patch publish hua par phone par kuch nahi | Phone us release line par nahi | `dumpsys` se phone version dekho; us version ka APK install ya `-ReleaseVersion` correct karo |
| `UnpatchableChangeException` (icons) | Release tree-shake ON tha, patch set alag | Us line ka full APK release dobara cut karo `-Mode release` (no-tree-shake), reinstall |
| Banner nahi dikha par patch laga | last-seen patch already match | normal; sirf naye patch par dikhta hai |
